    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver for anyone looking for utility over aesthetics. The exterior shows its age with several noticeable scratches, some minor door dings, and thinning clear coat on the hood. Inside, the upholstery has some visible staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster, though all electronics and climate controls remain fully functional. It has been mechanically maintained to ensure reliability, making it a solid choice for someone who needs a functional car despite its cosmetic imperfections.",
      "price": 19500.0,
