    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that can only be described as showroom-perfect. This specimen exhibits no signs of wear, reflecting a history of meticulous preservation and uncompromising care. Every aspect of the vehicle, from its flawless mechanical integrity to its pristine aesthetic state, meets the most rigorous standards of automotive excellence. This is a definitive opportunity for the discerning buyer seeking a vehicle in peerless condition.",
      "price": 44900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
